reviewText: Good graphics and accurate science behind this video that uses footage of war invasion scenes to demonstrate the activities of microorganisms in the human body.

I think everyone who has had a question about health issues they are experiencing should see this film. Your intestinal flora, your skin surfaces all are created by the microbes you receive from mom at birth.

I found the info in this film fascinating, from how to improve your dental health to how to get rid of digestive disorders.

Only one question: How is it that this film is listed as having come out in 1969???
